data.description: Welcome to Halifax. Renovated Ranch on corner lot in quiet neighborhood with access to Monponsett pond. New bedroom addition. Fireplace Living room. Laundry room. New heat, electrical and plumbing. New roof, siding and windows. New plaster walls, interior doors and trim. New ceramic tiled bath with double vanity. Great yard with new septic installed. Newer kitchen with new quartz counter top. Full basement and attic storage. More pictures to follow. All work to be completed prior to closing. Please call Listing agent for questions.
